{"tid":1946981,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個公司搞笑通告","createTime":"2020-03-28T03:44:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T04:48:35.000Z","uid":341683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1870cf5c2659e7fe653b1d24260caa2097f0cdcd","tid":1946981,"uid":341683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T03:44:02.000Z","msg":"公司出左份通告：<br />\n上班時請穿着合適服裝，不要穿短褲、破洞的牛仔褲、背心、運動衣服或人字拖鞋。<br />\n星期六員工可穿着整齊的運動衣服。<br />\n公司的服裝守則就是那麼簡單。<br />\n<br />\n結果第二日有人着連身短裙（唔係緊身架）返黎比人叫唔可以再着返黎，入面著左legging都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申返一份唔係office嘅工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e74f7254c71c718e97da073e9ccc63d12c84d10f","tid":1946981,"uid":205462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T03:59:51.000Z","msg":"睇嚟係著短裙嗰位小姐，對&quot;合適服裝&quot;嘅解讀，同正常人有少少分別 (腦細私人秘書另計)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09c9cdad41cab7fb5045258f19b75f6cce0e2024","tid":1946981,"uid":341683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e74f7254c71c718e97da073e9ccc63d12c84d10f","tid":1946981,"uid":205462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T03:59:51.000Z","msg":"睇嚟係著短裙嗰位小姐，對&quot;合適服裝&quot;嘅解讀，同正常人有少少分別 (腦細私人秘書另計)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:15:24.000Z","msg":"其實佢條裙唔算短<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知捉黎做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85e90601f3a947d0a5ef7935f3dd2d38fe76ca64","tid":1946981,"uid":138465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:33:49.000Z","msg":"成個月飯堂食三文治"},{"pid":"890d1fef64df0e99f8e69d2081e77216ff1ebe1b","tid":1946981,"uid":341683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85e90601f3a947d0a5ef7935f3dd2d38fe76ca64","tid":1946981,"uid":138465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T04:33:49.000Z","m